body:
This PR attempts to address @slava77's comment https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/10231#issuecomment-123015472 on the debug-ifdefs introduced in #10231. Most of the ifdefs are replaced with a new, locally-defined macro `IfLogTrace`, that has different definition depending if `EDM_ML_DEBUG` is defined or not.

Tested in CMSSW_7_6_X_2015-07-21-1100, no changes expected in results.

@rovere @VinInn
